Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.57,0:02:52.32,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,116)}Where does the truth lie for us？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.32,0:02:59.08,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,116)}象徴を失って迷い始める大衆よ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.16,0:03:03.71,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,116)}Trust in everything that you believe,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.71,0:03:06.84,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,116)}Living in this chaotic new world
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.84,0:03:10.17,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,116)}今、目を澄ます
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.17,0:03:13.72,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,116)}Trust in yourself not what they believe
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.72,0:03:17.01,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,116)}幻想の解の先へ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.01,0:03:22.02,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,116)}さあ騒然とノイズ　響く最中を
